#: fnprofile/templates/fnprofile/fnemail/login_notification_email.html:4
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"      Hello! %(username)s,\n"
"      You have logged in to FNSCHOOL:\n"
"      -- Login IP: %(login_ip)s\n"
"      -- Browser: %(HTTP_USER_AGENT)s\n"
"      If you are not logged in to FNSCHOOL, simply click on the link below "
"to log out:\n"
"      %(logout_url)s\n"
"      Or you can reset your password by clicking on the following link:\n"
"      %(reset_password_url)s\n"
"      Alternatively, you can click on the following link, and the FNSCHOOL "
"will log out of the currently logged-in session and reset your password for "
"you.\n"
"      %(generate_password_url)s\n"
"      (If the link does not redirect after clicking, please copy the entire "
"link into the browser address bar and press Enter.)\n"
"      Thank you for using FNSCHOOL!\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"您好！%(username)s,\n"
"　　您已经登录 FNSCHOOL：\n"
"　　-- 登录 IP：%(login_ip)s\n"
"　　-- 浏览器：%(HTTP_USER_AGENT)s\n"
"　　如果您未曾登录 FNSCHOOL ，点击以下链接即可退出登录：\n"
"　　%(logout_url)s\n"
"　　或者点击以下链接重置密码:\n"
"　　%(reset_password_url)s\n"
"　　或者，您也可以点击以下连接重新生成随机密码—— FNSCHOOL 会退出已登录的会"
"话，然后为您重新生成密码。\n"
"　　%(generate_password_url)s\n"
"　　（如果点击链接后无法跳转，请将链接复制到浏览器地址栏会按回车键以跳转）\n"
"　　谢谢您使用 FNSCHOOL 。\n"
"    "

